# This folder is for your story images

Place your image files here and reference them in your HTML like this:
<img src="images/your-image.jpg" alt="Description of image">

## Image Tips

- Use descriptive file names (e.g., `dark-forest.jpg` not `img1.jpg`)
- Keep images reasonably sized (800px width or less is usually good)
- Always add alt text that describes what's in the image
- Use JPG for photos, PNG for graphics with transparency

## Free Image Sources

If you need images, try these free sources:
- Unsplash: https://unsplash.com
- Pexels: https://pexels.com
- Pixabay: https://pixabay.com
